<p class="nx-mt-6 nx-leading-7 first:nx-mt-0">通过深入理解这些坐标系统及其转换，开发者可以更准确地控制射线的起点和方向，实现更精确的鼠标拾趣功能。这对于提高 3D 场景的交互性和用户体验至关重要。</p>
<h1 class="nx-mt-2 nx-text-4xl nx-font-bold nx-tracking-tight nx-text-slate-900 dark:nx-text-slate-100">Raycaster 原理与应用</h1>
<h2 class="nx-font-semibold nx-tracking-tight nx-text-slate-900 dark:nx-text-slate-100 nx-mt-10 nx-border-b nx-pb-1 nx-text-3xl nx-border-neutral-200/70 contrast-more:nx-border-neutral-400 dark:nx-border-primary-100/10 contrast-more:dark:nx-border-neutral-400">Raycaster 基础<a href="#raycaster-基础" id="raycaster-基础" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"></a></h2>
<p class="nx-mt-6 nx-leading-7 first:nx-mt-0"><code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">Raycaster</code> 是 Three.js 中用于实现鼠标拾趣的核心类，它通过模拟从相机发出的射线来检测与 3D 物体的交点。理解 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">Raycaster</code> 的工作原理对于开发交互式的 3D 应用至关重要。</p>
